WEBVTT

1
00:11:26.540 --> 00:11:29.400 
10块连个泡棉海豚都买不起
10? You can't even get a Foam Flipper with that.

2
00:11:29.400 --> 00:11:30.290 
何不赌50海豚币
Let's make it 50.

3
00:11:30.290 --> 00:11:31.320 
德哥  别这样
D.J., please.

4
00:11:31.820 --> 00:11:33.170 
50块现金怎么样
How bout 50 real ones?

5
00:11:33.170 --> 00:11:34.580 
好  那就5000美金
Okay. Make it five grand.

6
00:11:34.580 --> 00:11:35.670 
一下抬这么高吗
That's the jump?

7
00:11:36.530 --> 00:11:37.380 
为我赢下这场
Go win this for me.

8
00:11:37.390 --> 00:11:38.190 
好
Okay.

9
00:11:38.730 --> 00:11:39.760 
我们是同一队的
We're on the same team!

10
00:11:39.760 --> 00:11:41.530 
犯规  有人对我犯规
Foul! Somebody fouled me!

11
00:11:41.650 --> 00:11:42.740 
别假摔了
Stop flopping!

12
00:11:42.740 --> 00:11:43.940 
菲尔  加油  专注点
Phil, come on, man. Focus!

13
00:11:43.940 --> 00:11:45.470 
我们刚赌上了奥运金牌
We just bet our Olympic gold medals.

14
00:11:45.470 --> 00:11:48.120 
为什么  没人逼你做到这一步
Why? No one's making you do this!

15
00:11:52.960 --> 00:11:54.470 
我不想让你不自在
I hate that I made you uncomfortable.

16
00:11:54.470 --> 00:11:56.700 
我只是想让我们对彼此更真实
I-I just wanted us to be real with each other.

